name: onlyDuplicates

type.rawType: <U>(isEqualFn?: ((a: U, b: U) => boolean) | undefined) => <T extends U>(value: T, index: number, self: T[]) => boolean

value:
<U>(isEqualFn?: (a: U, b: U) => boolean) =>
  <T extends U>(value: T, index: number, self: T[]) => {
    return (
      self.findIndex((v) => (isEqualFn ? isEqualFn(v, value) : v === value)) !==
      index
    );
  }
